members.name: DOMPointReadOnly()
members.description: Defined to create a new DOMPointReadOnly object, but note that this constructor cannot be called by 3rd party JavaScript: doing so returns an "Illegal constructor" typeError.

members.name: DOMPointReadOnly.fromPoint
members.description: Translates the position/perspective of a DOMPoint to a new position (doesn't appear to be supported anywhere yet.)

members.name: DOMPointReadOnly.matrixTransform
members.description: Applies a matrix transform to a DOMPointReadOnly object (doesn't appear to be supported anywhere yet.)

members.name: DOMPointReadOnly.x
members.description: The x coordinate of the DOMPoint.

members.name: DOMPointReadOnly.y
members.description: The y coordinate of the DOMPoint.

members.name: DOMPointReadOnly.z
members.description: The z coordinate of the DOMPoint.

members.name: DOMPointReadOnly.w
members.description: The perspective value of the DOMPoint.
